  <ul class="comments by_rank" >
      
      <li class="ctsh clearfix" data-cid="11286371">
        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/secretmi/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1010310-66.jpg" alt="秘莫一" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/11286371/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/11286371/" class="">第62页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/secretmi/" class=" " title="秘莫一">秘莫一</a>
                (超级无敌海景粉蒸肉)
              
                <span class="allstar40" title="推荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="11286371">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">沤子，冬季使用的润肤品。
慈禧太后的沤子方内含防风、白芷、三柰、茯苓、白芨、白附子等，
共研粗渣，烧酒二斤将药煮透。去渣，兑冰糖、白蜜，合匀，候凉再兑冰片、朱砂面，搅匀，装瓷瓶内收。
</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2011-02-12 15:26</span>
                  
                    &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="">2人喜欢</span>
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                沤子，冬季使用的润肤品。<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>慈禧太后的沤子方内含防风、白芷、三柰、茯苓、白芨、白附子等，
<blockquote><q>共研粗渣，烧酒二斤将药煮透。去渣，兑冰糖、白蜜，合匀，候凉再兑冰片、朱砂面，搅匀，装瓷瓶内收。</q></blockquote>

                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
